This directory contains only public Sovereign OS update verification keys.

Each key uses two files with the same safe key identifier:

  <key-id>.pem   Ed25519 public key in PEM SubjectPublicKeyInfo format
  <key-id>.json  trusted metadata with algorithm, channels, and revoked status

No preview key is installed until release-key custody and rotation are approved.
An empty trust store fails closed and prevents update installation.
